description: It’s always important to have something worth fighting for, whether it’s an issue as big as equal rights or one as small as a raise in your allowance! The Riverdale kids are no strangers to making their voices heard when they want change. This digital exclusive collects two tales of Archie and friends taking on the establishment—and each other!
name: Civil Chore

description: Even as the Forever People more openly display their power, Lex Luthor and President Amanda Waller watch news reports of Superman’s actions with a nervous sense that humans are no longer in control.
name: Genesis - Part 2 of 9

description: It's a proud day for Cyborg when he grows his very first mustache! But what happens when said mustache becomes a sentient being bent on turning Cyborg into...an adult?!
name: My Little Mustache
Prisoner of the Plantman; Witchcraft in the Wax Museum

description: The blood hungry hordes of the Nadir are on the march, led by the invincible warlord Ulric. All that stands between them and victory is the fortress of Dros Delnoch. But the once mighty citadel of the Drenai empire is now a shell, its vastly outnumbered defenders demoralized and sensing defeat. As doom and despair threaten the Drenai, one man answers the call to arms; one man whose reputation alone can turn the tide... Druss the Legend.
name: GN

volume.name: David Gemmell's Legend: A Graphic Novel
